    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "tox screen\n, alcohol level\nfingerstick glucose\ndrug levels as indicated (ex.\nantiepileptic\nlevel if possible ingestion)\nHead CT\nif concern for trauma or mass lesion\nLumbar Puncture\nin most cases unless etiology is known\nEEG if possibly\nseizure\nrelated",
