    "Management": {
      "text": "most postinfectious cerebellitis self limited, resolve within 3 months without sequelae\ntox ingestion: supportive. social work or DCFS as indicated\nGuillain Barre\nadmit for IVIG, observation of respiratory status\nMeningitis\n/\nEncephalitis\nadmit, IV antibiotic, see meningitis section\nintracranial mass\n: neurosurgery consultation",
